Package de.dennisfalk.homeconnect2semp.model.semp.sempMessage

Class MessageType

java.lang.Object
de.dennisfalk.homeconnect2semp.model.semp.sempMessage.MessageType
public class MessageType extends Object
This type encapsulates information about an error or event. It can also be used for data-tunnelling. In this case only the Type and Data elements might be set.
